          <div property="content:encoded" class="field-item even"><p>Yesterday, the Drupal Security team <a href="https://www.drupal.org/SA-CORE-2014-005">announced that all Drupal 7 sites are highly vulnerable to attack</a>. Acquia deployed a platform-wide "shield" which protects all our customer sites, while still keeping them 100% functional for visitors and content editors. These sites can now <a href="http://docs.acquia.com/articles/drupal-7x-sa-core-2014-005-critical-security-update">upgrade to 7.32</a> in a more calm, controlled timeline. </p></div>
